Legendary creature art: A grotesquely charming, vaguely humanoid elemental resembling a Christmas poo – Mr. Hankey – stands amidst blades of grass, with swirling green and black mana symbols. It’s surrounded by a cycle of life and death, a lush green battlefield and a darkly humorous depiction of decomposition and rebirth, evoking a surreal, slightly unsettling, and ultimately festive atmosphere, digital painting, intricate details, magic the gathering style.